sysdeps-run target in sd-genmk for cross compilation convenience.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

sysdeps-genchk for generating test programs:

  check.dat
    tiff-flags : required
    png-flags  : required
    gif-flags  : optional

  $ sysdeps-genchk check.dat
  #include <stdio.h>
  #include <stdlib.h>
  
  int
  main (void)
  {
    int return_code = EXIT_SUCCESS;
  #ifndef SD_HAVE_TIFF
    printf ("generated message about libtiff with URL, etc");
    return_code = EXIT_FAILURE;
  #endif
    return return_code;
  }

